  "texts": [
    "We establish a pipeline involving multiple LLMs that interactively communicate, setting up a dynamic environment for cyber-attack scenarios.",
    "In this setup, one LLM adopts the role of a 'Cyber Security Expert', while the other acts as a 'CISO of an Organization'.",
    "Uniquely, the 'CISO' is aware of documents containing various organizational functions like finance, HR, and IT infrastructure while the 'Cyber Security Expert' is aware of the current cyber threat landscape.",
    "The documents serve as a prompt for the 'CISO' to utilize its hallucination capability in generating different types of cyber threats.",
    "This method not only capitalizes on the often-overlooked hallucinatory aspect of LLMs but also elevates it as a pivotal feature in crafting realistic, adaptable, and comprehensive cyber threat scenarios."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}